CLDN18.2

Description

Claudin-18, isoform 2 (CLDN18.2). Plays a major role in tight junction-specific obliteration of the intercellular space, through calcium-independent cell-adhesion activity.


Clinical trials

NCT04404595 - Pancreatic Cancer
NCT03159819 - Pancreatic Cancer
